OL,5, The soft drink brand Lilt - famously   
OL,6, advertised for its "totally tropical   
OL,7, taste" - is being scrapped after 50    
OL,8, years and rebranded.                   
OL,10,FFrom Tuesday it will be known as Fanta 
OL,11,FPineapple & Grapefruit, according to   
OL,12,Fits owner the Coca Cola Company.       
OL,14,FThe firm stressed the drink's taste and
OL,15,Fingredients would not change.          
OL,17,FBut fans - many of whom appeared to    
OL,18,Fassociate Lilt with memories of their  
OL,19,Fyouth - took to social media to express
OL,20,Ftheir dismay.                          
